2020-08-17T08:12:54.000Z","msg":"如果有既話我會去投<br />\n投「集體拒絕」定「集體留任」我已經有清楚諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我唔會去攻擊投另一面既人"},{"pid":"6f01107c2a72d0a7689579779908cdd117a60a60","tid":2159781,"uid":19165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6eabda362326e81160f3d7e0d626f27658123370","tid":2159781,"uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"而家最好搞民間公投<br />\n入唔入議會都尊重個結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"辭唔辭完全唔係重點, 由頭到尾都係支那分化我地既策略, 同時buy time畀自己, 用公投一方面彰顯直接民意, 一方面塞住所有人把口, 唔會再有藉口受任何一方攻擊, 完美化解分化策略, 反將支那一軍"},{"pid":"a7a56c9a3d35a66bbf524dd296c39dce33f9ed6d","tid":2159781,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"079ec3356eed32d618d2199fbdf4f7db87f47bfd","tid":2159781,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eabda362326e81160f3d7e0d626f27658123370","tid":2159781,"uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"而家最好搞民間公投<br />\n入唔入議會都尊重個結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:12:54.000Z","msg":"如果有既話我會去投<br />\n投「集體拒絕」定「集體留任」我已經有清楚諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我唔會去攻擊投另一面既人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:48:44.000Z","msg":"尊重結果<br />\n服從結果<br />\n好似big雲姨咁退休就退休"},{"pid":"37d6a60958284789ded9eebae2190b494ebb33e4","tid":2159781,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f01107c2a72d0a7689579779908cdd117a60a60","tid":2159781,"uid":19165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6eabda362326e81160f3d7e0d626f27658123370","tid":2159781,"uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"而家最好搞民間公投<br />\n入唔入議會都尊重個結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-0